sub_title: Communications and CRM Lead at Hub Australia
summary: A communications, marketing and CRM professional with over 4 years of experience. Previously, I worked at Hub Australia building a premium coworking community in line with the future of work. Before Hub Australia, I worked in strategy and events across a broad range of clients such as Spotify, Australian Super, Mercedes Benz and White Pages. I’m an energetic self-starter with a burning desire to create bold, audacious work together.
